com.survivingwithandroid.weather.lib.provider

Interface IWeatherProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ForecastIOWeatherProvider, OpenweathermapProvider, WeatherUndergroundProvider, YahooWeatherProvider

    public interface IWeatherProvider
    Public interface that all the weather provider must implement. If you want to code your weather provider you have to implement this interface.
    Author:
    Francesco Azzola
